          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Ending the Sanctuary Capitol Policy Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes U.S. Capitol Police officers, in the performance of official duties, to make arrests and otherwise enforce immigration laws within the District of Columbia.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
